Package: congressTools
Title: Simple Utility Functions for Working with Congressional Data
Version: 0.9.2
Authors@R: person("Alexander", "Furnas", email = "zfurnas@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simple utility functions for working with U.S. Congressional data.
    Convert between calendar years and Congress numbers, and standardize
    congressional district identifiers across different naming formats.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1)
Imports:
    stringr (>= 1.3)
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
